ygData.messageBody:
Tried using Carillion with a flute last night, no additional effect could be
seen. There might have been one, but it was slight if so, none of the
thirty or so groups I tried it on showed any change. Anyone see a change in
any other targeted instrument songs?

Also, did anyone else notice that their own footsteps increased in volume by
about a factor of 10 with the patch? I had to turn the sound down so that
environment noises like the crickets in Innothoule were silent before I
could stand the sound of my own footsteps. I still don't hear anything of
other people's/mob's footsteps. I asked around and it seemed that about two
thirds of the people experienced something similar. 15 of us in Steamfont
/bugged it for sure.

Kit
